@smxysu3 - Please follow the instructions for compiling on Ubuntu and let us know. 

http://twitter.github.io/heron/docs/developers/compiling/linux/#building-on-ubuntu-14.04:34fe9f2d9cc3cd7e319ca75e7da08332

and let us know

@longdafeng - you should not connect to maven.twttr.com. At the top of the repo - there is a WORKSPACE file, with the following entries - 

maven_server(
  name = "default",
  url = "http://central.maven.org/maven2/",
)

maven_server(
  name = "twitter-maven",
  url = "http://maven.twttr.com",
)

Remove the maven_server entry that has maven.twttr.com and try it. You should connect by default to maven central.
